<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="16Apr1933"><font color="red">16 April 1933</font> <i>NLHW</i> (from Paul L&eacute;on to Harriet Weaver): Mr Joyce &hellip; a very painful attack of colitis &hellip; He seems to have got into his mind that his health is definitely wrecked and his sight never to be repaired &hellip; he himself does nothing &hellip; to try and get started on his work. </div>
